"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-04-10-paris-2024-qualifier-why-super-falcons-beat-banyana-banyana-to-olympics-ticket-waldrum\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Super Falcons head coach Randy Waldrum has explained why his team beat the Banyana Banyana of South Africa to the 2024 Olympic Games ticket.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 44, \"end\": 57, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Randy Waldrum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Waldrum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nigeria earned a place at Paris 2024 at the expense of the reigning African champions after a 1-0 aggregate scoreline.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Waldrum claimed the Super Falcons beat their rivals to the ticket because of their defensive organisation.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were much more organised than the previous times we played them,\\\" Waldrum said after the game.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"South Africa talked a lot before these two matches, we just kept quiet.\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 490, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999455012599, \"rank\": 5.418269056050159e-08, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's why I felt confident.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe in our team and I knew we will be hard team to break down even with their talent.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The thing we would then hope is that you finish off one or two of your opportunities to advance and that is what we did.\\\"\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nigeria will slot into Group C at Paris 2024, joining Spain, Japan and Brazil.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_FIFA_U-17_Women's_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.7111369343641692, \"rank\": 0.30333505202477035, \"text\": \"Group C\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_FIFA_U-17_Women's_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_FIFA_U-17_Women's_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999856165102184, \"rank\": 1.428309996337148e-05, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http